   "summary": "MS Check - NP PDF Check",
   "description": "To be completed by: {{date}} \n\n NPrinting has one PDF. It can be found on the Guides page: \n http://rd-docloc.rdlund.qliktech.com/rc/en-US/nprinting/April2018/Content/Introduction/Guides.htm \n Download the pdfs using different browsers. \n Make sure that the (R) on the first two pages of the pdfs render as superscript \n Make sure the general layout is ok. For example check headers and footers for unwanted line breaks. \\n Make sure image fit on page/are not too small. \\n Make sure the master page usage is correct. \\n Make sure the numbering of chapters and TOC is ok. \n Make sure table breaks look good. \n Make sure the ToolbarIcon font renders. \n Make sure that the title of the document matches the front page. \n Make sure that the version numbers correspond: Inside documentation; on cover and in footers, in the different outputs (can only be checked after build engineer has implemented) \n Make sure that no old version numbers are used, by searching for Nprinting throughout the document.",
   "issuetype": {
      "name": "Task"
   }
  }
}

